{"type": "article", "id": 7410, "title": "Audi 竞技自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-16T07:21:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234438QlXj8bC6Jnk3dUPE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t在刚刚过去的日内瓦汽车展上，奥迪展示了他们的第一款竞技自行车，车身采用的是 T-1000 碳化纤维，与 R18 e-tron Quattro 采用的是同一材料。整个自行车只有 13 磅的自重，强调轻盈和运动性能，且外观线条流畅，时尚大方。不过价格也十分“大方”，目前售价为 18400 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234436NEqSxf7z1PRcjAdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234436E1lZ2vuemFa6s4P0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344361FjmPyp3edouKiM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344375ceI30fLVw8JiHDN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}